---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Process — How We Build Profitable Client Acquisition Systems | BrandsBuilders',
  description:
    'Our process focuses on financial logic first, fixing system leaks second, and scaling only when profit is controlled and measurable.',
  canonical: 'https://brandsbuilders.agency/process'
};
---

<Layout seo={seo}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-slate-950 text-white py-20 lg:py-28 border-b border-slate-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold mb-6">
        How we approach growth
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed">
        Growth is not a tactic problem. It is a systems and economics problem.
        Our process exists to prevent wasted spend and build profit-first acquisition.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Principle -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-slate-900">
        The core principle
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        We do not start with ads, websites, or channels.
        We start by understanding whether acquiring customers can be profitable
        given your margins, capacity, and constraints.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Phases -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

      <!-- Phase 1 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Phase 1</p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3 text-slate-900">
          Financial clarity
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          We assess ticket size, margins, fulfillment capacity, and constraints
          to define what acquisition can realistically support.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 2 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Phase 2</p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3 text-slate-900">
          System correction
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          We identify and fix leakage across messaging, routing, tracking,
          and follow-up before increasing traffic or spend.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Phase 3 -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Phase 3</p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mb-3 text-slate-900">
          Controlled scale
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Once profit is proven and attribution is clean,
          we introduce scale deliberately without breaking efficiency.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ownership -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 text-slate-900">
        Ownership & control
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        You own all assets, accounts, data, and decisions.
        We operate with delegated access and document systems
        so you are never locked in.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Guarantee -->
  <section class="bg-slate-950 text-white py-20 border-t border-slate-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-6">
        About the performance guarantee
      </h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Our engagements include a profit-based guarantee under clearly defined conditions.
        If profit is not achieved, we extend the work at no cost.
        If results still do not materialize, a full refund applies.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl text-center">
      <p class="text-slate-700 text-lg mb-8">
        The consultation determines whether this process makes sense for your business.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/apply"
        class="inline-block px-8 py-4 border border-slate-600 rounded-lg text-slate-900 hover:border-slate-900 transition"
      >
        Apply for a Consultation →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
